                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">Situations When Bike Ownership Transfer Is Needed</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Sale of a used bike to another person</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>Transfer within family (gift or inheritance)</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>Ownership transfer due to death of registered owner</strong></li>
