                                <td>Manual follow-up</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <p class="bikecarhub-tip"><span class="font-weight-700">BikeCarHub Recommendation:</span> Opt for the online method if your RTO supports it. It's more transparent and hassle-free.</p>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">How to Track Application Status</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Visit <a href="https://vahan.parivahan.gov.in/" class="for-link" target="_blank">Parivahan Vehicle Services</a></li>
                    <li>Click on "Application Status"</li>
                    <li>Enter <strong>Application Number</strong> and <strong>Date of Birth</strong></li>
                    <li>Status shows: "Pending", "Under Process", "Approved", or "RC Dispatched"</li>
                </ul>
                <p>You may also receive SMS or email updates from the RTO portal.</p>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">FAQs about Bike Ownership Transfer</h2>

                <div class="accordion" id="faqBikeTransfer">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q1">
                                1. Can I transfer ownership without the original RC?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                No. You must have the original RC. If lost, apply for a duplicate RC before transferring.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q2">
                                2. How long does it take to complete the process?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Generally, 7-15 days for online transfer. It may take longer for inter-state transfers.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q3">
                                3. Is physical presence of the vehicle required at the RTO?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                For some RTOs, yes—especially in case of address change or re-registration.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q4">
                                4. Can I transfer ownership of a bike with an active loan?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                No. First, clear the loan and remove hypothecation by submitting Form 35 and NOC.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q5">
                                5. Do both buyer and seller need to be present?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Not always. Some RTOs accept e-signed documents or Aadhaar eKYC. Others may ask for both.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q6">
                                6. Can I transfer ownership if the bike is older than 15 years?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, but ensure the fitness certificate is renewed before transfer.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q7">
                                7. Is NOC required for same-state transfers?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Not usually. NOC is only required when transferring between states.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q8">
                                8. Can I check ownership details online?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, use <a href="https://vahan.parivahan.gov.in/" class="for-link" target="_blank">vahan.parivahan.gov.in</a> to check ownership status using registration number.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q9">
