                        <div id="q9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                The original owner remains legally responsible for the bike, including insurance and traffic penalties.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="q10">
                                10. Can I do the transfer through mParivahan app?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="q10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqBikeTransfer">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                No. The app shows details, but the actual transfer is done through the Parivahan portal.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
